{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0001", "text": "我這樣強悍 我這樣硬朗 我對着你那輕佻 怎麼不懂反抗", "structure": {"line_index": 1, "char_count": 23}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 5, 2, 0, 2, 5, 5, 2, 2, 5, 5, 4, 2, 5, 5, 3, 0, 9, 3, 3, 9, 9, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ngo5", "ze5", "joeng6", "koeng4", "hon6", "ngo5", "ze5", "joeng6", "ngaang6", "long5", "ngo5", "deoi3", "zoek6", "nei5", "naa5", "hing1", "tiu4", "zam2", "mo1", "bat1", "dung2", "faan2", "kong3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這樣", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "強悍", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這樣", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "硬朗", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "對", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "着", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "那", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "輕佻", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "怎麼", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "懂", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "反抗", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "犯賤", "artists": ["陳小春"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1875", "prev_line_id": null, "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0002", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0002", "text": "我這樣強壯 卻這樣陪葬 愛你就似個信仰 再痛也會嚮往", "structure": {"line_index": 2, "char_count": 23}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 5, 2, 0, 4, 4, 5, 2, 0, 4, 4, 5, 2, 5, 4, 4, 5, 4, 4, 5, 4, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ngo5", "ze5", "joeng6", "koeng4", "zong3", "koek3", "ze5", "joeng6", "pui4", "zong3", "oi3", "nei5", "zau6", "ci5", "go3", "seon3", "joeng5", "zoi3", "tung3", "jaa5", "hoeng3", "wong5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這樣", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "強壯", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "卻", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這樣", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "陪葬", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "愛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "就", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "似個", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "信仰", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "再痛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "也", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "會", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "嚮往", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "犯賤", "artists": ["陳小春"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1875", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0001", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0003", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0003", "text": "我將畢生威武放低 做塊階磚給你墊底 未算低 未算低", "structure": {"line_index": 3, "char_count": 22}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 3, 3, 3, 3, 5, 4, 3, 2, 4, 3, 3, 3, 5, 4, 9, 2, 4, 3, 2, 4, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ngo5", "zoeng1", "bat1", "sang1", "wai1", "mou5", "fong3", "dai1", "zou6", "faai3", "gaai1", "zyun1", "kap1", "nei5", "din3", "dai2", "mei6", "syun3", "dai1", "mei6", "syun3", "dai1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "將", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "畢生", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "威武", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "放", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "低", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "做塊", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "階磚", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "給", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "墊底", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "未算", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "低", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "未算", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "低", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "犯賤", "artists": ["陳小春"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1875", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0002", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0004", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0004", "text": "若你想我吠 我將畢生機智放低 做個階梯給你上位", "structure": {"line_index": 4, "char_count": 21}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 5, 9, 5, 2, 5, 3, 3, 3, 3, 4, 4, 3, 2, 4, 3, 3, 3, 5, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["joek6", "nei5", "soeng2", "ngo5", "fai6", "ngo5", "zoeng1", "bat1", "sang1", "gei1", "zi3", "fong3", "dai1", "zou6", "go3", "gaai1", "tai1", "kap1", "nei5", "wai6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "若", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "想", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "吠", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "將", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "畢生", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "機智", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "放", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "低", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "做個", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "階梯", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "給", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "上位", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "犯賤", "artists": ["陳小春"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1875", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0003", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0005", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0005", "text": "話到底 辯駁完全無謂", "structure": {"line_index": 5, "char_count": 9}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 4, 9, 2, 4, 0, 0, 0, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["waa6", "dou3", "dai2", "bin6", "bok3", "jyun4", "cyun4", "mou4", "wai6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "話", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "到底", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "辯駁", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "完全", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "無謂", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "犯賤", "artists": ["陳小春"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1875", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0004", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0006", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0006", "text": "別笑我 我犯賤 被嫌棄 也像蜜甜 別勸我 我自願", "structure": {"line_index": 6, "char_count": 19}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 4, 5, 5, 2, 2, 2, 0, 4, 5, 2, 2, 0, 2, 4, 5, 5, 2, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["bit6", "siu3", "ngo5", "ngo5", "faan6", "zin6", "bei6", "jim4", "hei3", "jaa5", "zoeng6", "mat6", "tim4", "bit6", "hyun3", "ngo5", "ngo5", "zi6", "jyun6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "別笑", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "犯賤", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "被", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "嫌棄", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "也", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "像", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "蜜甜", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "別", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "勸", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "自願", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "犯賤", "artists": ["陳小春"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1875", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0005", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0007", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0007", "text": "下來這條賊船 別理我 我犯賤 被磨折 也是自然", "structure": {"line_index": 7, "char_count": 19}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 0, 5, 0, 2, 0, 2, 5, 5, 5, 2, 2, 2, 0, 4, 5, 2, 2, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["haa6", "loi4", "ze5", "tiu4", "caak6", "syun4", "bit6", "lei5", "ngo5", "ngo5", "faan6", "zin6", "bei6", "mo4", "zit3", "jaa5", "si6", "zi6", "jin4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "下來", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "條", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "賊船", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "別理", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "犯賤", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "被", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "磨折", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "也", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "自然", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "犯賤", "artists": ["陳小春"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1875", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0006", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0008", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0008", "text": "別救我 我自願 並無怨言", "structure": {"line_index": 8, "char_count": 10}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 4, 5, 5, 2, 2, 2, 0, 4, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["bit6", "gau3", "ngo5", "ngo5", "zi6", "jyun6", "bing6", "mou4", "jyun3", "jin4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "別救", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "自願", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "並", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "無", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "怨言", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "犯賤", "artists": ["陳小春"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1875", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0007", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0009", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0009", "text": "你那樣無理 卻最具人氣 我喪盡理智愛你", "structure": {"line_index": 9, "char_count": 17}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 5, 2, 0, 5, 4, 4, 2, 0, 4, 5, 3, 2, 5, 4, 4, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["nei5", "naa5", "joeng6", "mou4", "lei5", "koek3", "zeoi3", "geoi6", "jan4", "hei3", "ngo5", "song1", "zeon6", "lei5", "zi3", "oi3", "nei5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "那樣", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "無理", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "卻", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "最具", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "人氣", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "喪盡", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "理智", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "愛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "犯賤", "artists": ["陳小春"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1875", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0008", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0010", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0010", "text": "都只得到跟尾 你接近完美 我接近麻痹", "structure": {"line_index": 10, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 9, 3, 4, 3, 5, 5, 4, 2, 0, 5, 5, 4, 2, 0, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["dou1", "zi2", "dak1", "dou3", "gan1", "mei5", "nei5", "zip3", "gan6", "jyun4", "mei5", "ngo5", "zip3", "gan6", "maa4", "bei3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "都", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "只", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "得到", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "跟", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "尾", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "接近", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "完美", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "接近", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "麻痹", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "犯賤", "artists": ["陳小春"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1875", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0009", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0011", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0011", "text": "我要用最痛那裏 領教你那真理", "structure": {"line_index": 11, "char_count": 13}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 4, 2, 4, 4, 5, 5, 5, 4, 5, 5, 3, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ngo5", "jiu3", "jung6", "zeoi3", "tung3", "naa5", "leoi5", "ling5", "gaau3", "nei5", "naa5", "zan1", "lei5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "我要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "用", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "最痛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "那裏", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "領教", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "那", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "真理", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "犯賤", "artists": ["陳小春"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1875", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0010", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0012", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0012", "text": "未曾惹人愛憐 對 我犯賤 被流放 也像樂園 別勸我", "structure": {"line_index": 12, "char_count": 20}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 0, 5, 0, 4, 0, 4, 5, 2, 2, 2, 0, 4, 5, 2, 2, 0, 2, 4, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["mei6", "cang4", "je5", "jan4", "oi3", "lin4", "deoi3", "ngo5", "faan6", "zin6", "bei6", "lau4", "fong3", "jaa5", "zoeng6", "lok6", "jyun4", "bit6", "hyun3", "ngo5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "未曾", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "惹人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "愛憐", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "對", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "犯賤", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "被", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "流放", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "也", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "像", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "樂園", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "別", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "勸", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "犯賤", "artists": ["陳小春"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1875", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0011", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTg3NQ_0013", "paragraph_id": "para_05"}}
